  ('jee-physics-electromagnetic-waves-m01', 'jee-physics-electromagnetic-waves', 'Electromagnetic Waves', '**Electromagnetic (EM) waves** are self-sustaining oscillations of electric and magnetic fields that travel through vacuum.

