  ('jee-chemistry-environmental-chemistry-m01', 'jee-chemistry-environmental-chemistry', 'Environmental Chemistry', '**Environmental chemistry** studies pollutants and the chemical processes in air, water and soil.

## Air Pollution
| Pollutant | Source / effect |
| --- | --- |
| CO | Incomplete combustion; binds haemoglobin |
| SO2, NOx | Burning fuel; acid rain |
| CFCs | Aerosols; ozone depletion |

