  ('gate-core-cs-computer-organization-architecture-m01', 'gate-core-cs-computer-organization-architecture', 'Computer Organization & Architecture', '**Computer organization** covers how the CPU, memory and pipelines execute instructions — a calculation-heavy GATE topic.

