  ('gate-core-cs-artificial-intelligence-ml-basics-m01', 'gate-core-cs-artificial-intelligence-ml-basics', 'Artificial Intelligence & ML Basics', '**Artificial intelligence** builds agents that perceive and act; **machine learning** lets them improve from data.

