  ('gate-programming-ds-linked-lists-stacks-queues-m01', 'gate-programming-ds-linked-lists-stacks-queues', 'Linked Lists, Stacks & Queues', '**Linked lists, stacks and queues** are linear structures with distinct access rules — staple GATE data-structure questions.

