  ('jee-physics-current-electricity-q01', 'jee-physics-current-electricity', 'A 12 V battery drives 3 A through a resistor. The resistance is:', '0.25 ohm', '4 ohm', '15 ohm', '36 ohm', 'B', 'By Ohm''s law R = V/I = 12/3 = 4 ohm.', 0),
