  ('jee-physics-magnetism-emi-q03', 'jee-physics-magnetism-emi', 'A charge moving parallel to a magnetic field experiences a force of:', 'Zero', 'Maximum', 'qvB', 'qE', 'A', 'F = qvB sin(theta); when v is parallel to B, theta is zero so the force vanishes.', 2),
