  ('jee-mathematics-matrices-determinants-q06', 'jee-mathematics-matrices-determinants', 'A matrix that equals its own transpose is called:', 'Skew-symmetric', 'Singular', 'Symmetric', 'Orthogonal', 'C', 'A matrix with transpose equal to itself is symmetric.', 5),
