  ('jee-chemistry-biomolecules-polymers-q01', 'jee-chemistry-biomolecules-polymers', 'Glucose is classified as a/an:', 'Disaccharide', 'Amino acid', 'Polysaccharide', 'Aldohexose', 'D', 'Glucose is an aldohexose, a six-carbon monosaccharide with an aldehyde group.', 0),
