  ('jee-chemistry-biomolecules-polymers-q04', 'jee-chemistry-biomolecules-polymers', 'Nylon-6,6 is an example of which polymer type?', 'Addition polymer', 'Condensation polymer', 'Natural polymer', 'Elastomer', 'B', 'Nylon-6,6 forms by condensation, releasing water at each amide linkage.', 3),
