  ('jee-chemistry-biomolecules-polymers-q07', 'jee-chemistry-biomolecules-polymers', 'Denaturation of a protein destroys its higher structure but keeps the:', 'Catalytic activity', 'Quaternary structure', 'Primary sequence', 'Tertiary fold', 'C', 'Denaturation unfolds the protein but leaves the primary amino acid sequence intact.', 6),
