  ('jee-chemistry-metallurgy-q02', 'jee-chemistry-metallurgy', 'Heating a carbonate ore to give the oxide is called:', 'Roasting', 'Calcination', 'Smelting', 'Leaching', 'B', 'Calcination heats a carbonate in limited air to drive off carbon dioxide.', 1),
